        <h3>Co-founder of Prismatica</h3>
        <p>
          In March 2019, I co-founded Prismatica (formerly "New Regions"), a horizontal queer-feminist 
          initiative based in Mahilow, Belarus. We became the first LGBTQ+ initiative in the regions of 
          Belarus, working to create safe and inclusive environments through educational and cultural events.
        </p>
